data.description: Voila! Behold the house you have been waiting for all year long. This turn-key single family home is centrally located in the heart of historic Garnerville. Just a stone throws from the Palisades Interstate Parkway, Ferry access to NYC, Bear Mountain Bridge, shops, restaurants, hiking trails, the Marina & state parks. This immaculate colonial style home boasts top to bottom, inside & outside renovations galore! Nestled on a cul-de-sac full of festive cheer. Enjoy the ease of cooking in your open concept chef's kitchen. Entertain in your luxurious living room & dining room. Host comfortably in your fully finished basement that showcases a spare room, bathroom, movie room, den & laundry. Your oasis awaits you w/ a huge resort style pool & fenced in yard. Meticulously renovated, with no detail spared! Additional storage w/ pantry, insulated attic & shed. Long Driveway for parking. Extremely low taxes. No HOAs. Not a Condo. Come make this house your home by saying yes to the address today!
